The present invention may be better understood, and its numerous objects, features, and advantages made apparent to those skilled in the art by reference to the accompanying drawings, in which the use of the same reference symbols in different drawings indicates similar or identical items.


FIG. 1 shows a cross sectional view for illustrating a PIP-type capacitor structure which is utilized in a logic circuit or analog circuit according to the prior art;


FIG. 2 shows a cross sectional view for illustrating a MIM-type capacitor structure which is utilized in a logic circuit or analog circuit according to the prior art;


FIG. 3 shows a cross sectional view for illustrating a MIM-type capacitor structure which is utilized in a logic circuit or analog circuit according to the present invention;


FIGS. 4a to 4f show cross sectional views for illustrating various steps of a method which is for manufacturing a capacitor shown in FIG. 3.
